dct_title_s: Property belonging to the estate of Robert Annett. Dec'd, in Bergen County, N.J., showing the division thereof among his heirs
dct_description_sm: Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Created by Robert C. Bacot, George Huyler, and William A. Wood
Surveyer L.W. Post noted that dots on map indicate where iron pins, spikes or marks on a rock are located from the survey.
The name I. Zabriskie has been added to the map
